@node Introduction "SmartMedian: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   SmartMedian is a plugin for the famous image-manipulation-program
   ArtEffect2/3+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect's
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   SmartMedian is a median-filter that blurs a picture without loosing sharp
   edges. It can remove noise visible in large equal areas and leaving details
   untouched. It is well suited to remove moirÈs from scanned printings without
   smoothing the details out. Very useful if natural pictures are mixed with
   artifical graphics/text, e.g. cover of a CD. 
   Medianfilter of this type are sometimes known as despeckle filters.

   There is another similar plugin available: SmartBlur

@endnode

